&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sales experience in Bone, Biologics, and Cartilage or equivalent in the Extremities surgical specialty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and collaboratively within a team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational, communication, and relationship-building skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced, field-based sales environment&lt;/li&gt;
