&lt;li&gt;Coordinate outbound shipments to customers or other facilities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure&amp;nbsp;all shipping documentation is&amp;nbsp;accurate&amp;nbsp;and up to date.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
